      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. The exterior maintains a strong shine, though you may find a few small stone chips on the hood and minor surface marks from regular driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics functioning properly and only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is mechanically sound, drives smoothly, and represents a great balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal for its next owner.",
