    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and has been kept clean and well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
