    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This driver-focused example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels through the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, mitigating common platform weaknesses. Performance remains sharp thanks to a well-maintained suspension geometry that preserves the 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack feedback. While the car shows signs of careful use, the powertrain exhibits excellent thermal management and linear power delivery, making it a prime candidate for the technical enthusiast seeking a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
