    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my reliable set of wheels that has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014I'm honestly going to miss it! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin! \u2728",
      "price": 32000.0,
