    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical structural preventive maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. The chassis is tuned with an upgraded coilover setup for enhanced lateral grip and reduced body roll. While the exterior displays honest patina expected of a driver\u2019s car, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience with a focus on tactile feedback and mechanical harmony.",
